Musimy   teraz   napisaę  Startup-Sequence.   Sekwencja  powinna  wyglâdaę
nastëpujâco:

MakeDir RAM:T RAM:ENV RAM:C
Copy >NIL: ENVARC: RAM:ENV ALL NOREQ
Assign >NIL: ENV: RAM:ENV
Assign >NIL: T: RAM:T
Copy >NIL: C:Copy RAM:C
Copy >NIL: C:Delete RAM:C
Copy >NIL: C:Lha RAM:C
